

Usage :

 x  # create a user
    user = CronIo::User.create(name, email, password)

 .. # list the cron.io jobs of a user
    CronIo::Cron.list(user)

    # create a cron.io job for a user
    CronIo::Cron.create(user, name, url, schedule)

    # retrieve the details of a given cron.io job
    CronIo::Cron.get(user, id)


TO TEST :
- Cron#list timeouts if invalid credentials
